Author: alexvilis
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: Risk Of Fake Profiles In Social Networks And Freelance Platforms https://medium.com/@ecta/risk-of-fake-profiles-in-social-networks-and-freelance-platforms-53f70079073  In the United States alone, freelancers are expected to become the workforce majority within just ten years. Companies benefit greatly from these independent contractors, since it allows them to search for talent in all corners of the globe instead of being limited to their city. This is particularly true for companies searching for AI/IoT/blockchain developers, who can all do their jobs remotely. One of the biggest challenges facing companies when it comes to finding this valuable talent? The prevalence of fake profiles on social media channels and freelance platforms.  In order to cut out the aforementioned middleman, many companies will skip using recruiters and third-parties and search for developers on freelance platforms as well as social media channels like LinkedIn and Twitter. However, it’s only too easy to get scammed by someone who doesn’t have any true tech skills.  These candidates tout fake experience to match the needs of the company’s job listing or inquiry. They might also go as far as to use fake certificates in order to “back up” their skill set and put the company at ease.  The same goes for developers who are looking for valid AI/IoT/blockchain projects. With even more limited resources, it can be difficult to distinguish between a fake job listing and a legitimate opportunity. This can often lead them down a rabbit hole that results in no job, time lost, and potentially even stolen personal information. However, current technology has no solution for this issue, or sifting through the endless amount of fake profiles both for candidates and for companies.

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: Firstly thank you for your interest in our project. At this point we can't talk in details about marketing and business growth strategy, but let's reveal some of crucial things in short.. We allocated 13% of tokens for Marketing and Bounty and 13% for Platform growth. We have collaboration with educational institutions to track achievements of their students, and in that way they will be able to mine ECTA SKILLS and be ready for employment. If you have done your own research, you already know that ECTA is backed by Slovenian Government, and some parts of our of marketing and growth strategy is associated with them. We are working on whitepaper improvement, especially on token economics and ECTA Pay utility. All details will be disclosed soon, but I can reveal to you that we are planing to enable ECTA Pay transfer to fiat/tether and vice verse, also in plan is to integrate payment card for ECTA users. If you look at the crypto space, you have to agree that most trusted platform definitely is Ethereum. Nothing is set in the stone yet, we also considering other platforms and with some of them we are negotiating. Please stay tuned, in front of us is a very exciting time for ECTA. You can join our telegram group and other social medias, here's links below. Telegram https://t.me/ectaplatform Facebook https://www.facebook.com/ectaplatform/ Reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/ectaplatform/ Twitter https://twitter.com/Ecta_io Blog https://medium.com/@ecta Announcement Channel @ectanews

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: ECTA network is generally combined product consisted of AI prooven tools which our team member successfully launched in previous products  + Blockchain which we will develop at our Faculty for Computer Science. The blockchain has two tokens: ECTA PAY and ECTA SKILLS token. ECTA PAY is internal payment utility token (fungible) and ECTA SKILLS is token confirming your skills (non-fungible).  AI will save an enormous time and raise efficiency. How? Simply because it would match two parties together with the highest probability for productive outcome. So you as company for an example describe your needs and AI engine connects you with the person who can fullfill your needs as developer. How will AI know who is best? By analyzing education, profession, skills, and others, and the most exciting thing is that there will be ECTA SKILLS token which is proving that the person you connect with is genuine and has critical experience to help you in task execution.

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: ECTA will transform way how people Claim - Prove - Discover - Own - Hire SKILLS in a digital age by focusing on the fastest growing industries such as Blockchain, AI, and IoT and mainly targeting on the low-middle income country population (2B unbanked).  Our protocol is geared by two token types:  ECTA PAY (fungible ERC20) and ECTA SKILLS (non-fungible, non-transferable ERC 721). On the basis of smart contract ECTA Pay tokens will enable seamless payment solution, contracting and protection between the developers on one side and client (company) on another side.  ECTA SKILLS non-fungible token’s purpose is holding a person’s (e.g. IT developer) accredited skill certificate/endorsement, which he/she will gain (mint) by successfully executing an agreed task, which is than approved by the contractor of the task. Each ECTA non-fungible token will hold the definition of a skill required by a successful task execution. One person can thus gain or mint multiple ECTA non-fungible tokens, with which he/she proves his competences. Since these ECTA non-fungible tokens are devoted to only a specific person, for his performed work, he/she should not and thus cannot transfer this earned token to any other person. This will be technically solved by not implementing the transfer function of the ERC721 standard and furthermore by storing the initial receiver’s information into the ECTA non-fungible token’s internal data (struct).  We are legally organized as a cooperative called "Distributed Collective" with an address in Slovenia.  ECTA is endorsed officially by the Ministry of Technology of Slovenia (letter) and we won the government tender of "Solving the problems of precarious freelance workers in Slovenia" whereby ECTA provides the solution locally prior to going global upon crowdsale. Moreover, our concept is endorsed by UN in New York as it addresses Sustainable Development Goals and helps in talent discovery and boosting of employability especially in low-middle income countries.

Body: ECTA (Efficient Collaboration Team Autonomous) is the first blockchain-based trust protocol for global employability of developers (AI, Blockchain and IoT).The concept, empowered by the proven AI tools, aims to solve the inefficiencies related to the time loss, verification of online profiles, talents discovery (especially in the low-middle income countries) and safe way to conduct business (payment solution with the power of smart contracts).While working on ECTA platform, besides collecting their earnings in ECTA PAY tokens (ERC20) developers are having a unique possibility to earn (mine) ECTA SKILLS non-fungible/non-transferable tokens (ERC721) as a reward for every task completed -which serve as proof of their skills and boosting of reputation among others.AI component of the platform helps companies worldwide to discover and employ these developers in a safe and productive way for both sides.

Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: This platform is not an experiment to be built from scratch but assembled as a result of our teams dedicated work over the past 10 years. ECTA takes advantage of the experience gained and components from the products we have already created, including ARK Blockchain, Edu-CTX, and Eventregistry. Bringing together this knowledge and expertise, we integrate hard-fought lessons and technologies into a product that will bring value to many lives.

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: ECTA (Efficient Collaboration Team Autonomous) is the first blockchain-based trust protocol for global employability of developers (AI, Blockchain and IoT).  The concept, empowered by the proven AI tools, aims to solve the inefficiencies related to the time loss, verification of online profiles, talents discovery (especially in the low-middle income countries) and safe way to conduct business (payment solution with the power of smart contracts).  While working on ECTA platform, besides collecting their earnings in ECTA PAY tokens (ERC20) developers are having a unique possibility to earn (mine) ECTA SKILLS non-fungible/non-transferable tokens (ERC721) as a reward for every task completed -which serve as proof of their skills and boosting of reputation among others.  AI component of the platform helps companies worldwide to discover and employ these developers in a safe and productive way for both sides.  ECTA non-fungible token's purpose is holding a person's (e.g. IT developer) accredited skill certificate/endorsement, which he/she will gain (mint) by successfully executing an agreed task, which is than approved by the contractor of the task. Each ECTA non-fungible token will hold the definition of a skill required by a successful task execution. One person can thus gain or mint multiple ECTA non-fungible tokens, with which he/she proves his competences. Since these ECTA non-fungible tokens are devoted to only a specific person, for his performed work, he/she should not and thus cannot transfer this earned token to any other person. This will be technically solved by not implementing the transfer function of the ERC721 standard and furthermore by storing the initial receiver's information into the ECTA non-fungible token's internal data (struct).

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: We have already the first case (user) of ECTA and it is government of Slovenia. Thats how it all started actually. We as experts under cooperative "Distributed Collective" were awarded from the Ministry of Technology of Slovenia to make platform for all workers in Slovenia who don't work on "permanent" basis when employed but get hired for the specific tasks as freelancers. Those workers once they are hired struggle to manage their hiring process in terms of time and costs because there is no efficient and affordable solution to manage their payrolls, book keeping, social contributions, etc. We are launching ICO in order to make our solution scalable to others as well as adopted with crypto payments solutions. The workers who are non employed on permanent basis is the growing problem and ECTA will solve it.

Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: Yes. Employers will have tool to discover, analyze, compare and best part of it not with a time loss and uncertainty but with the AI engine of ECTA platform which will provide them all those utilities on one place. Yes, developers will mined their ECTA SKILLS tokens like "credit score" and thanks to that become visible and genuine. Alibaba started using reputation scores 20 years ago ECTA aims to do the same just with global employability marketplace!  ECTA Team

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: The solution is very simple but with a multi-level approach. As holder of ECTA PAY tokens you become a member of the platform. We will import your KYC and generate your ECTA profile in partnership with CIVIC. As the second step you describe your idea or the project you want to realize. Afterwards ECTA AI tools connect developers with the complementary skills which are optimal in terms of price, timing, and skills to make your idea come true. You will have on your dashboard a possibility to add new developers (team members) as your project grows and demands additional skills for further realization. This process will enable you to create your (E)fficient (C)ollaboration (T)eam (A)utonomous powerfull unit called ECTA.

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: The concept, empowered by the proven AI tools, aims to solve the inefficiencies related to the time loss, verification of online profiles, talents discovery (especially in the low-middle income countries) and safe way to conduct business (payment solution with the power of smart contracts).While working on ECTA platform, besides collecting their earnings in ECTA PAY tokens (ERC20) developers are having a unique possibility to earn (mine) ECTA SKILLS non-fungible tokens (ERC721) as a reward for every task completed -which serve as proof of their skills and boosting of reputation among others. AI component of the platform helps companies worldwide to discover and employ these developers in a safe and productive way for both sides.

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: Hello goyubiwub, a valuable relationship will be reached because individuals and developers won't loose a time in finding each other like nowadays - thanks to the existing ECTA AI algorithms which will learn about needs of individuals and skills from developers and as a result put them together to work. Thanks to ECTA pay (fungible) tokens the unbanked developers worldwide won't struggle to collect their earnings for the services provided to individuals/companies. Also, when developers mine ECTA skills (non-fungible) tokens as the proof of services completed they will be more visible to other individuals/companies because their reputation will grow and they won't be suspicious to the future parties which want to hire them. So all process is open, intuitive, anti-fraudulent and rewarding. ECTA Team

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: For discovering of new talents ECTA especially focuses on low-middle income countries like nobody else. ECTA AI engine detects and tracks individuals which demonstrated a certain achievements in terms of education, awards, initiatives, volunteering, cross-collaboration, publications, workshops, etc. (see our AI algorithm from www.eventregistry.org) Additionally, once the talent is discovered he will be notified and offered to increase his KYC what will enable him to collaborate with ECTA and become fully visible and "employable" to the parties in demand for him. ECTA Team

Author: LivDamone
Title: 🔵📣 [ANN] ECTA | First Blockchain Trust Protocol For Global Employability 🔵📣
Body: No. The platform is not an experiment going to be built from scratch after completed ICO but rather the product which is result of hard, long, dedicated and tested work by our team for the last 10 years. We will use components and know-how from the products already created by our team such as ARK, Edu-CTX, Eventregistry, etc. Thanks to blockchain we are able to integrate each component with another in synergy with AI tools and thus create an ecosystem of digital utilities which will serve to masses. We need ICO not just because of funds. Yes we need to pay the bills during the stages of development thats true but an ultimate goal of ICO is to distribute ECTA tokens to masses and by doing so to create sort of "petrol stations" where you can buy the "fuel" to benefit on using the ECTA platform no matter of you geographical presence, language and banking status. Inequalities will be reduced because everyone will have a chance to show his talent, provide services, create a value which will be recorded on the blockchain. Also, the platform will be multi-lingual.  ECTA Team
